title: Make This Brand New 1 Bedroom In Unique Historic Building Yours Today!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Your search stops here at the brand new Millworks Lofts where you will find affordable luxury living near Downtown Minneapolis.', 'Our community is located on Hiawatha, just a couple steps away from the 38th Street Blue line Light Rail Platform.', 'Surrounding the community is a neighborhood filled with charming family-owned stores and restaurants.', 'Enjoy fabulous amenities like geothermal heating, fitness center, community room and a rooftop deck featuring skyline views.', 'Your apartment will be brimming with modern finishes like stainless steel appliances, washers and dryers in every unit, and quartz kitchen countertops.', 'Be the first person to live in a brand new loft, apply online today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Oversized windows', '- Kitchen bar or movable island (Select Homes)', '- Covered parking available (Call For Details)', '- Washer & dryer in EVERY apartment home', '- Large walk-in closets', '- Close to public transportation', '- Modern, polished concrete flooring throughout', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Millworks Lofts participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Wednesday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Millworks Lofts', '4041 Hiawatha Avenue South', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55406', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'NmLSJbW4zMp']
